            <bindingDesc>
              <binding>
                <p>Lacquered boards. On the outside covers, two plants with large, red flowers on an orange field with a frame of small flowers on black. On the inside covers, a large, gold sprinkled, yellow flower on a black field with a gilt frame.</p>
              </binding>
            </bindingDesc>
